by the exact piecewise quarter-chain greedy cost. -/
theorem chromaticNumberNat_induce_le_quarterChainGreedyColorCost
    (n : тДХ) (G : LabeledGraph n)
    (hG : G тИИ quarterChainIndependentBlockEvent n)
    (hblock : 1 тЙд quarterChainSteps n) :
    тИА U : Finset (Fin n),
