    exact hdiff
  ┬╖ intro x hx
    rw [hint] at hx
    exact hlower x hx

/-! ## Trapping a target-matching tilt -/

/-- Endpoint mean brackets trap a target-matching point in the same open
interval when the mean map is strictly increasing. -/
